<CHAPTER ID=10> Intermodality and intermodal freight transport <SPEAKER ID=269 NAME=" President " > The next item is the report ( A5-0358/2000 ) by Mrs Poli Bortone , on behalf of the Committee on Regional Policy , Transport and Tourism , on the communication from the Commission to the European Parliament , the Council and the Economic and Social Committee on the progress of the implementation of the action programme of the communication on intermodality and intermodal freight transport in the European Union .
